OL,6,FActor John Alford has been found
OL,7,Fguilty of sexually assaulting two
OL,8,Fteenage girls during a party at a
OL,9,Ffriend's home.
OL,11,FThe 53-year-old was charged with four
OL,12,Fcounts of sexual activity with a 14-
OL,13,Fyear-old girl and charges of sexual
OL,14,Fassault and assault by penetration
OL,15,Frelating to a 15-year-old girl at a
OL,16,Fproperty in Hertfordshire on April 9,
OL,17,F2022.
OL,19,FAlford denied all of the charges.
