OL,12,Fhome of a third girl whose father was
OL,13,Ffriends with Alford.
OL,15,FThe former actor bought around #250
OL,16,Fworth of alcohol, food, and cigarettes
OL,17,Ffrom a nearby petrol station in the
OL,18,Fearly hours of the morning.
OL,20,FThis included a bottle of vodka, which
OL,21,Fthe victims subsequently drank.
